.TH "LIGHTNING-BACKUP" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-backup \- composer over FEAT-174 + FEAT-185
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning backup
[\fIsubcommand\fR] [\fIargs\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.nf
lightning backup — composer over FEAT-174 + FEAT-185.

Implements FEAT-187.

By default: emits a fresh SCB, auto-commits the snapshot,
pushes the wallet repo. `--seed` ALSO writes an encrypted
seed export into the wallet repo (default off; seed lives
in the operator's head normally).
.fi
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.BR lightning (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Part of the \fBlightning\fR educational Lightning Network frontend.
